    "body_en": "<p style=\"text-align: justify; \">Elderly: A word that encompasses the old and the weak. One more thing has been added here.</p> <p style=\"text-align: justify; \">Notion abbreviation, that is, a person who is not proficient in using Notion, an online collaboration tool. This is a nickname given to my colleagues in an environment where most work is done using this tool.</p> <p style=\"text-align: justify; \">I laughed a lot when I first heard it, but I felt frustrated by the discomfort caused by words that should not be used for entertainment and the reality of many weak people created by many technologies.</p> <div class=\"cheditor-caption-wrapper\" style=\"text-align: center;\"> <figure class=\"cheditor-caption\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); background-color: #d97706; margin: 0px; display: inline-block; width: 660px;\"><img alt=\"notion. JPG\"src=\"https://www.artinsight.co.kr/data/tmp/2302/20230201043049_nfvhbaab.jpg\" style=\"width: 660px; height: 419px;\"/> <figcaption class=\"cheditor-caption-text\" style=\"margin: 6px 10px 6px 10px; text-align: left; line-height: 18px; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: -0.04em; text-align:justify;\">Notion</figcaption> </figure> </div> <p>There is one huge advantage I felt after entering the IT field. The point is that they are somewhat free from digital aging compared to others (Digital Aging: It is considered a solution for the digitally weak, who appear to become more vulnerable to digital technology as they age.).</p> <p>It is similar to saying that my friends who are elementary, middle, and high school teachers are good at new word quizzes, or that sociology professors prepare to go to work by playing Melon Top 100, which can be considered the exclusive domain of young people. He is still able to naturally acquire the latest technology, so he is ahead of his peers in this area.</p> <p><br/></p> <p>However, even within the same field, there are many people who feel the same gap as my colleagues. Even when the physical world was everything, the world was wide, but when I looked around the online and metaverse world, the world became infinitely wider.</p> <p>The speed at which technology is developed is faster than the speed at which technology is learned, and the news of new technologies pouring out every day is faster than I thought, so there is nothing I can do. In other words, there are times when acquiring these skills does not seem natural to me and seems burdensome.</p> <p><br/></p> <p>It would be a lie if I said I only felt curious when I first encountered Open AI?셲 ?쏞hatGPT,??an AI chatbot equipped with GPT-3.5, or ?쏮idjourney,??an AI tool that creates images matching keywords based on Discord. I felt tired from the pressure of having to learn this skill.</p> <p>Then why not just live the way you used to live? A very comfortable sound. Many people do not access this tool out of interest. Use it intensively in your work. Through conversations with ChatGPT, not only can you easily gain insight through images created by Midjourney, but you can also lay the foundation for actual commercial work.</p> <p>That's right. In this era where I have become a product, not being able to utilize these things can be measured at some point as a decrease in productivity.</p> <div class=\"cheditor-caption-wrapper\" style=\"text-align: center;\"> <figure class=\"cheditor-caption\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); background-color: #d97706; margin: 0px; display: inline-block; width: 398px;\"><img alt=\"midjourney. JPG\"src=\"https://www.artinsight.co.kr/data/tmp/2302/20230201042842_ivnmbgdw.jpg\" style=\"width: 398px; height: 419px;\"/> <figcaption class=\"cheditor-caption-text\" style=\"margin: 6px 10px 6px 10px; text-align: left; line-height: 18px; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: -0.04em; text-align:justify;\">midjourney</figcaption> </figure> </div> <p>This was a comment on an article that said a company introduced AI to its human resources department and laid off employees.: ?쏧 expected AI to take my job away, but not in this way.?쒲 also thought that AI would change work, but not in this way.</p> <p>I thought my share would be divided into what AI can do and what it cannot do, and I thought a project team would be formed when collaborating with AI. I never thought we would become so closely, personally, and organically intertwined.</p> <div class=\"cheditor-caption-wrapper\" style=\"text-align: center;\"> <figure class=\"cheditor-caption\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); background-color: #d97706; margin: 0px; display: inline-block; width: 660px;\"><img alt=\"entomo.jpg\"src=\"https://www.artinsight.co.kr/data/tmp/2302/20230201043815_whphcwlz.jpg\" style=\"width: 660px; height: 372px;\"/> <figcaption class=\"cheditor-caption-text\" style=\"margin: 6px 10px 6px 10px; text-align: left; line-height: 18px; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: -0.04em; text-align:justify;\">entomo</figcaption> </figure> </div> <p>The way I relieve stress is by getting rid of the things that are pressuring me, and this never ends.</p> <p>There are many people who are already skilled in these techniques that I only discovered last month. Voluntary learning ability is entering the realm of talent. If you used to find people who get certifications as a hobby fascinating, now you have to follow them. No, you need to collect a daily list of new technologies before learning them.</p> <p><br/></p> <p>The word that the standards for competency are changing is becoming widely known.?쁀pplication??rather than ?쁲torage??is not only required in creativity tests. In other words, we live in an era where people who know how to use a smartphone's phone book or how to use an application that organizes business cards after taking pictures are more popular than people who can memorize phone numbers.</p> <p>The advent of the new technological era does not just expand the meaning of words such as the elderly. It is being overthrown. More than we expected. Improvisation is not a fleeting thing, but is becoming a daily thing. Collect and organize rather than memorize, utilize rather than control, and face rather than anticipate.</p> <div class=\"cheditor-caption-wrapper\" style=\"text-align: center;\"> <figure class=\"cheditor-caption\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); background-color: #d97706; margin: 0px; display: inline-block; width: 660px;\"><img alt=\"digital visiting card.jpg\"src=\"https://www.artinsight.co.kr/data/tmp/2302/20230201043630_izsenmkn.jpg\" style=\"width: 660px; height: 372px;\"/> <figcaption class=\"cheditor-caption-text\" style=\"margin: 6px 10px 6px 10px; text-align: left; line-height: 18px; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: -0.04em; text-align:justify;\">Digital Visiting Card</figcaption> </figure> </div> <p>Explosive changes are taking place in the term ?쁝lienation?? I, and we, have no choice but to ?쁝dapt?? I take a deep breath, but I can't help but look through IT news and trend letters again.</p> <p>I was resentful of why we had fallen into the era of great revolutions such as the agricultural revolution and the industrial revolution, which are one of the few inflection points that humanity faces, but then I brought my vision back to reality. It is also a time of great stimulation. With new technologies flashing before our eyes, there is no time to feel bored, so I think addiction to stimulation may be the cause of humanity's extended lifespan.</p> <p><br/></p> <p>It hasn't been long since digital alienation began to receive attention, but it will spread throughout society, and no one has any choice but to be a digital underdog in a specific field.</p> <p>I hope everyone will let go of the pressure because even IT students like me and people in the field find this pace too much. I hope you enjoy using it. Like my colleagues, I hope to always ask questions, try things out, and share new knowledge.</p> <p>With new technology, it is time to make way for a new word to replace the term 'old and weak'.</p> ",
