    "body_en": "<p style=\"text-align: justify; \">Are there moments when it feels awkward to open your mouth? Do you need to organize what you want to say before making a phone call? If you think about it, we are all phonosapiens (holding our smartphones away from our bodies) who are more comfortable typing than speaking. It may be an unending Anthropocene.</p> <p>Human relationships are also changing as the main form of communication moves from volatile face-to-face conversations to text messages such as messengers. Lying in bed and reminiscing about conversations Instead, you can scroll up and down the message window on your smartphone to see the exact remaining letters again.</p> <p>This can affect the sustainability of relationships and is changing the very framework of human relationships. It will.</p> <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"3.jpg\" src=\"https://www.artinsight.co.kr/data/tmp/2110/20211001024701_gfkxxryh.jpg\" style=\"width: 480px; height: 270px;\"/></p> <p>What were we talking about with the person next to us before that?</p> <p>On the way to meet and break up with a friend all day long, it was clearly fun, but the words I can't remember, the emotions are just floating around, but I get drunk and go back to my friends. I used to go back. But, what if it?셲 text? A gap is created between the time of thinking and the time of typing, and the content is refined. So, there are people who prefer text over conversation.</p> <p>Not only that, The text is kept to a minimum, excluding tone, gestures, and facial expressions. An economical method of conversation may be preferred because it requires less effort. The disadvantage in this area is This is clearly evident: according to Hidden Hearing, a hearing care company in the UK, 40% of adults think for a long time about the meaning behind the message, have experienced misunderstanding a joke, and even 33% have quit the relationship. Even You can also easily find a checklist to check your texting habits.</p> <p>To alleviate this problem, emoticons are being actively developed. Being able to convey blunt words smoothly using various characters, You can also just express your facial expressions without words. It was effective to try to reduce the constraints of flat text even though it was still a 2D environment.</p> <p>Not only pictures, By introducing emoticons with added movement, the text conversation method is improved rather than reduced, and is still different from the face-to-face conversation method. It's getting farther away.</p> <p style=\"text-align: center; \"><img alt=\"techblogbox.jpg\" src=\"https://www.artinsight.co.kr/data/tmp/2110/20211001024909_eronoume.jpg\" style=\"width: 660px; height: 368px;\"/></p> <p style=\"text-align: justify; \">The Hidden Hearing survey results mentioned earlier show that 75% of adults mentioned the importance of face-to-face conversation. This may be why video meeting functions, including video lectures, are improving day by day.</p> <p style=\"text-align: justify; \">Meanwhile, Just as video platforms including TikTok and YouTube cannot give up text in the form of comments, Since text is still the most efficient way to communicate, it is important for Phonosapiens to develop and adapt to additional improvements such as emoticons. It seems essential.</p> ",
